oversell [our] results regarding the negative impact of the residence MW
 on rents.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 While that negative coefficient is consistent with our model where raising
 local prices decrease housing demand, we do not provide any direct evidence
 in favor of this channel.
 One reason for that is data availability: we are not aware of price indexes
 dissagregated at the ZIP code level.
 (Referee 1 suggests using survey data such as PSID or CEX.
 Referee 2 suggests using price data from Diamond and Moretti 2023.
 These datasets vary at the much broader geography: the commuting zone.)
 We will re-write the introduction and the results section to qualify these
 results.
