\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
The first comment by R3 is that assuming perfectly flexible adjustments
 in the intensive margin of housing demand (as we do) seems contradictory
 with the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

short-run
\begin_inset Quotes erd
